description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if, for any date between January 27 and March 31, 2026, the US Dollar - Korean Won (USD/KRW) pair has a daily "High" value equal to or above 1,500.00. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source for this market is Investing.com — specifically, the USD/KRW daily “High” values published under “Historical Data” at https://www.investing.com/currencies/usd-krw-historical-data.

This market will resolve once final data for March 31, 2026 has been published. If data for March 31, 2026 has not been published by April 7, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve based on the available data at that time.
